        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2011-07-28 17:05:09.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nCurrent osc_send_oap_rpc() only allow partial page at the end of file, I think this patch will make 'hole' in the RPC.\n\nActually, I think the redundant page copy for lockless io must be avoided at the end, and this is just a temporary solution to avoid data corruption. Given that, I think the patchset 1 solution is simpler and cleaner.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
